&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>When I was small, I used to cry for toys, &lt;br>
My parents gave me those &lt;br>
I played with those toys, very seriously &lt;br>
So seriously that if someone hides them &lt;br>
or break them I will create huge unrest in the family &lt;br>
I will cry from the top of my voice &lt;br>
And let others know what unjust has happened to me.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>